    <title>typora配合hexo时图片显示问题</title>
    <url>/2023/12/16/typora%E9%85%8D%E5%90%88hexo%E6%97%B6%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<ol>
<li><p>配置typora</p>
<p>perference—image—When Insert配置如下</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p><img src="/2023/12/16/typora%E9%85%8D%E5%90%88hexo%E6%97%B6%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/image-20231216201841414.png" alt="image-20231216201841414"></p>
<ol>
<li><p>添加hexo插件</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install https://github.com/CodeFalling/hexo-asset-image --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p>启用hexo配置</p>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">post_asset_folder:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p>清除并重启</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo g &amp;&amp; hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>生效</p>
<p><img src="/2023/12/16/typora%E9%85%8D%E5%90%88hexo%E6%97%B6%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/image-20231216202135619.png" alt="image-20231216202135619"></p>
